      "title": "Anura Kumara also decided to act",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "JVP's MP Vijitha Herath has announced that People's Liberation Front leader Anurakumara Dissanayake will contest in the vote to be held in Parliament to elect the President and will file his nomination.",
        "Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe, Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa, former Minister of Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna Dalus Alagaperuma and Field Marshal Sarath Fonseka were reported to be contesting."
      ],
